      &lt;p style="font-size: 1.05rem;"&gt;
        Strategic territory has &lt;strong&gt;${isLow ? 'high' : 'some'} local value&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Üí local actors ${isLow ? '' : 'may'} fight to control it&lt;br&gt;
